description:
This data set is composed of enthalpy of mixing measurements made for binary mixtures of alcohols, ethers, ketones, alkanes, and esters (+ acids).

The measurements were all made at close to ambient conditions, and in almost all cases for three different compositions: 25%, 50% and 75%.

This data set was originally curated as part of the test set for the `expanded` study as part of the `binary-mixture` project
